==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Whaling
<hw>Whal"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to, or employed in, the
pursuit of whales; <as>as, a <ex>whaling</ex> voyage; a <ex>whaling</ex>
vessel.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

